Terms and Conditions
====================

“SixPL” is used as a trading name of SixPL LLC and Digitalimpulse Online Private Limited. All the business activities conducted on this website is done under the name of "iPib Edttech LLC" or “Digitalimpulse Online Private Limited.”

Terms used in the website, such as “We” / “Us” / “Our” or “Company” individually or collectively refers to as "SixPL LLC" or "Digitalimpulse Online Private Limited" and terms such as “You” / “Your” / “Yourself” indicates our users on this website.

The page is dedicated to lay down the terms and conditions under which visitors to our website must abide. It is required for you to read the terms and conditions carefully. In any case, if you are not accepting the same we humbly request you to exit the site. Further, the terms are conditionally revised as per the business providers, associates, companies or subsidiaries. You must keep a track of this page from time to time.

USE OF WEBSITE CONTENT
----------------------

You may not sell or modify any content on this website be it logos, brands, marks headings, labels, names, signatures, numerals, shapes or any combinations. All of the mentioned content is either owned or are used under license by the website. So the use of any of these mentioned content or properties except that is provided, is strictly prohibited.

ACCEPTABLE WEBSITE USE
----------------------

### General Rules

The website must not be used in order to transmit, distribute, store or destroy material as it can constitute or encourage any act that constitutes a criminal offence or violates any applicable law or regulation. Also, it will damage the copyright, trademark, trade secret or other intellectual property rights of others or violate the privacy or publicity or other personal rights of others.

### Limitation Of Liability

As per the conditions user agrees that the company shall not be liable for any damages arising from interruption, suspension or termination of service, including but not limited to direct or/and indirect or/and incidental or/and special consequential or/and exemplary damages, whether such interruption or/and suspension or/and termination was justified or not, negligent or intentional, inadvertent or intentional.

User further agrees that the Company shall not be responsible or liable for any statements or conduct of any third party of the service. In such a case Company’s total liability to the User for all damages or/and losses or/and causes of action exceed the amount paid by the User to Company, if any, that is related to the cause of action.

### DISCLAIMER OF DAMAGES

The Company or any parties, organizations or entities associated with the corporate brand name us or otherwise, mentioned at this Website is not liable for any damages including, without limitations, incidental and consequential damages, lost profits, or damage to computer hardware or loss of data information or business interruption which is a result of resulting fro the use or inability to use the Website and the Website Material, whether based on warranty, contract, tort, or any other legal theory, and whether or not, such organization or entities were advised of the possibility of such damages.

Contact Information
-------------------

### USA Headquarter

SixPL  
SixPL LLC  
16192 Coastal Highway  
Lewes, DE 19958  
Phone: +1 779 545 2612  

### India Delivery Center

SixPL  
Digitalimpulse Online Private Limited  
M 138, 2nd Floor, Connaught Place  
New Delhi, India - 110001  
Phone: +91 9318484366
